#. <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.51" id="51"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: pabhassaravaggo (bj) | accharāvaggo (s3)
msgctxt "an1.51-60:0.2"
msgid "6. Accharāsaṅghātavagga"
msgstr "6. Fingersnap"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:0.3"
msgid "51"
msgstr "51"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc51.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:51.1.1"
msgid "“Pabhassaramidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr "“This mind, mendicants, is radiant."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:51.1.2"
msgid "Tañca kho āgantukehi upakkilesehi upakkiliṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr "But it is corrupted by passing corruptions."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:51.1.3"
msgid "Taṃ assutavā puthujjano yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr "An uneducated ordinary person does not truly understand this."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:51.1.4"
msgid "Tasmā ‘assutavato puthujjanassa cittabhāvanā natthī’ti vadāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"So I say that ‘the uneducated ordinary person has no development of the "
"mind’.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:51.1.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.52" id="52"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:51.1.6"
msgid "52"
msgstr "52"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc52.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:52.1.1"
msgid "“Pabhassaramidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr "“This mind, mendicants, is radiant."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:52.1.2"
msgid "Tañca kho āgantukehi upakkilesehi vippamuttaṃ."
msgstr "And it is freed from passing corruptions."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:52.1.3"
msgid "Taṃ sutavā ariyasāvako yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "An educated noble disciple truly understands this."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:52.1.4"
msgid "Tasmā ‘sutavato ariyasāvakassa cittabhāvanā atthī’ti vadāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"So I say that ‘the educated noble disciple has development of the mind’.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:52.1.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.53" id="53"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:52.1.6"
msgid "53"
msgstr "53"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc53.1"></a>
#. VAR: mettācittaṃ → mettaṃ cittaṃ (bj) | mettacittaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an1.51-60:53.1.1"
msgid "“Accharāsaṅghātamattampi ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu mettācittaṃ āsevati;"
msgstr ""
"“If, mendicants, a mendicant cultivates a mind of love even for the time of "
"a finger snap,"

msgctxt "an1.51-60:53.1.2"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave:"
msgstr "they’re called"

msgctxt "an1.51-60:53.1.3"
msgid ""
"‘bhikkhu arittajjhāno viharati satthusāsanakaro ovādapatikaro, amoghaṃ "
"raṭṭhapiṇḍaṃ bhuñjati’."
msgstr ""
"a mendicant who does not lack absorption, who follows the Teacher’s "
"instructions, who responds to advice, and who does not eat the country’s "
"alms in vain."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:53.1.4"
msgid "Ko pana vādo ye naṃ bahulīkarontī”ti."
msgstr "How much more so those who make much of it!”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:53.1.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.54" id="54"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:53.1.6"
msgid "54"
msgstr "54"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc54.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:54.1.1"
msgid "“Accharāsaṅghātamattampi ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu mettācittaṃ bhāveti;"
msgstr ""
"“If, mendicants, a mendicant develops a mind of love even for the time of a "
"finger snap,"

msgctxt "an1.51-60:54.1.2"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave:"
msgstr "they’re called"

msgctxt "an1.51-60:54.1.3"
msgid ""
"‘bhikkhu arittajjhāno viharati satthusāsanakaro ovādapatikaro, amoghaṃ "
"raṭṭhapiṇḍaṃ bhuñjati’."
msgstr ""
"a mendicant who does not lack absorption, who follows the Teacher’s "
"instructions, who responds to advice, and who does not eat the country’s "
"alms in vain."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:54.1.4"
msgid "Ko pana vādo ye naṃ bahulīkarontī”ti."
msgstr "How much more so those who make much of it!”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:54.1.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.55" id="55"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:54.1.6"
msgid "55"
msgstr "55"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc55.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:55.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Accharāsaṅghātamattampi ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu mettācittaṃ manasi karoti;"
msgstr ""
"“If, mendicants, a mendicant focuses on a mind of love even for the time of "
"a finger snap,"

msgctxt "an1.51-60:55.1.2"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave:"
msgstr "they’re called"

msgctxt "an1.51-60:55.1.3"
msgid ""
"‘bhikkhu arittajjhāno viharati satthusāsanakaro ovādapatikaro amoghaṃ "
"raṭṭhapiṇḍaṃ bhuñjati’."
msgstr ""
"a mendicant who does not lack absorption, who follows the Teacher’s "
"instructions, who responds to advice, and who does not eat the country’s "
"alms in vain."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:55.1.4"
msgid "Ko pana vādo ye naṃ bahulīkarontī”ti."
msgstr "How much more so those who make much of it!”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:55.1.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.56" id="56"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:55.1.6"
msgid "56"
msgstr "56"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc56.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:56.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye keci, bhikkhave, dhammā akusalā akusalabhāgiyā akusalapakkhikā, sabbe te "
"manopubbaṅgamā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, whatever qualities are unskillful, part of the unskillful, on "
"the side of the unskillful, all of them are preceded by the mind."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:56.1.2"
msgid "Mano tesaṃ dhammānaṃ paṭhamaṃ uppajjati, anvadeva akusalā dhammā”ti."
msgstr "Mind arises first, and unskillful qualities follow right behind.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:56.1.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.57" id="57"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:56.1.4"
msgid "57"
msgstr "57"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc57.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:57.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye keci, bhikkhave, dhammā kusalā kusalabhāgiyā kusalapakkhikā, sabbe te "
"manopubbaṅgamā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, whatever qualities are skillful, part of the skillful, on the "
"side of the skillful, all of them are preceded by the mind."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:57.1.2"
msgid "Mano tesaṃ dhammānaṃ paṭhamaṃ uppajjati, anvadeva kusalā dhammā”ti."
msgstr "Mind arises first, and skillful qualities follow right behind.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:57.1.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.58" id="58"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:57.1.4"
msgid "58"
msgstr "58"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc58.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:58.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannā vā "
"akusalā dhammā uppajjanti uppannā vā kusalā dhammā parihāyanti yathayidaṃ, "
"bhikkhave, pamādo."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to unskillful "
"qualities, or makes skillful qualities decline like negligence."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:58.1.2"
msgid ""
"Pamattassa, bhikkhave, anuppannā ceva akusalā dhammā uppajjanti uppannā ca "
"kusalā dhammā parihāyantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you’re negligent, unskillful qualities arise and skillful qualities "
"decline.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:58.1.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.59" id="59"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:58.1.4"
msgid "59"
msgstr "59"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc59.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:59.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannā vā kusalā "
"dhammā uppajjanti uppannā vā akusalā dhammā parihāyanti yathayidaṃ, "
"bhikkhave, appamādo."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to skillful "
"qualities, or makes unskillful qualities decline like diligence."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:59.1.2"
msgid ""
"Appamattassa, bhikkhave, anuppannā ceva kusalā dhammā uppajjanti uppannā ca "
"akusalā dhammā parihāyantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you’re diligent, skillful qualities arise and unskillful qualities "
"decline.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:59.1.3"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.60" id="60"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:59.1.4"
msgid "60"
msgstr "60"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc60.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.51-60:60.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannā vā "
"akusalā dhammā uppajjanti uppannā vā kusalā dhammā parihāyanti yathayidaṃ, "
"bhikkhave, kosajjaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to unskillful "
"qualities, or makes skillful qualities decline like laziness."

msgctxt "an1.51-60:60.1.2"
msgid ""
"Kusītassa, bhikkhave, anuppannā ceva akusalā dhammā uppajjanti uppannā ca "
"kusalā dhammā parihāyantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you’re lazy, unskillful qualities arise and skillful qualities decline.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:60.1.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.51-60:60.1.4"
msgid "Accharāsaṅghātavaggo chaṭṭho."
msgstr ""
